### SG-036 P1-core-update — 11 endpoint coverage 보강 (Cycle 10, 2026-05-12)
###
### 배경:
###   Cycle 10-A (71): P1-read 10 추가 → 79 unique 예상.
###   본 cycle (72): P1-core-update 25건 중 첫 11건 (PUT 위주) 보강.
###   목표: 79 → 90 unique, mismatch 126 → 115 (11 감소).
###
### Scope:
###   P1-core-update 25건 중 11건 — 모든 entity 의 PUT (DELETE 는 Cycle 11).
###   특히 PATCH/PUT method 정합 검증 (Type D drift 측정 — tables/active_deck).
###
### Schema 정합 (BO src/models/schemas.py 기준):
###   각 RequestModel 은 `{Resource}Update` 형태 (optional 필드).
###   RBAC: require_role("admin") (대부분).
###
### Cycle 10 update matrix (P1-core-update 11건 / PUT 위주):
###   1. PUT /api/v1/series/{id}
###   2. PUT /api/v1/competitions/{id}
###   3. PUT /api/v1/players/{id}
###   4. PUT /api/v1/users/{id}
###   5. PUT /api/v1/blind-structures/{id}
###   6. PUT /api/v1/payout-structures/{id}
###   7. PUT /api/v1/flights/{id}
###   8. PUT /api/v1/events/{id}
###   9. PUT /api/v1/configs/{id}
###  10. PATCH /api/v1/decks/{id}             (router 가 PATCH 사용)
###  11. PUT /api/v1/tables/{id}              (Type D drift 검증 — .http 는 PATCH 가 있을 수 있음)
###
### Type D drift (router PUT ↔ .http PATCH) 명시:
###   - tables/{id}: router=PUT, .http history 에 PATCH 존재 → 본 cycle 에서 PUT 추가.
###   - tables/{id}/active_deck: 동일 패턴. 별도 cycle 11 에서 보강.
###
### 잔여 (Cycle 11+ 분할):
###   - DELETE 14건 (blind-structures, competitions, events, flights, payout-structures, players, series, users, skins, tables/seats, blind-structures/levels)
###   - blind-structures/{id}/levels/{id} PUT/DELETE
###   - tables/{id}/seats/{id} PUT/DELETE
###
### Source: SG-036 Spec_Gap_Registry §4.5

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

@series_id = {{$dotenv TEST_SERIES_ID}}
@competition_id = {{$dotenv TEST_COMPETITION_ID}}
@player_id = {{$dotenv TEST_PLAYER_ID}}
@user_id = {{$dotenv TEST_USER_ID}}
@blind_structure_id = {{$dotenv TEST_BLIND_STRUCTURE_ID}}
@payout_structure_id = {{$dotenv TEST_PAYOUT_STRUCTURE_ID}}
@flight_id = {{$dotenv TEST_FLIGHT_ID}}
@event_id = {{$dotenv TEST_EVENT_ID}}
@config_id = {{$dotenv TEST_CONFIG_ID}}
@deck_id = {{$dotenv TEST_DECK_ID}}
@table_id = {{$dotenv TEST_TABLE_ID}}

### 72.1 PUT /api/v1/series/{id} — update series (admin only)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/series/{{series_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "series_name": "WSOP 2026 Main Event — Updated",
  "end_at": "2026-07-16T23:59:59Z"
}

# 예상 응답:
# 200 OK + ApiResponse[SeriesResponse]
# 404 = SERIES_NOT_FOUND. RBAC: admin only.

### 72.1b PUT /api/v1/series/{id} — viewer 거부 (403)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/series/{{series_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "series_name": "Should fail"
}

# 예상 응답: 403 Forbidden, AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE.

### 72.2 PUT /api/v1/competitions/{id} — update competition (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competition_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "WSOP 2026 — Updated"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[CompetitionResponse].
# RBAC: admin only.

### 72.3 PUT /api/v1/players/{id} — update player (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/players/{{player_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nationality": "United States",
  "country_code": "US"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[PlayerResponse].

### 72.4 PUT /api/v1/users/{id} — update user (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "display_name": "Updated Operator Name",
  "role": "operator"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[UserResponse].
# RBAC critical: admin only. password 변경은 별도 endpoint.

### 72.5 PUT /api/v1/blind-structures/{id} — update blind structure (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{blind_structure_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Blind Structure",
  "levels": [
    { "level": 1, "small_blind": 100, "big_blind": 200, "ante": 0, "duration_minutes": 20 },
    { "level": 2, "small_blind": 200, "big_blind": 400, "ante": 0, "duration_minutes": 20 }
  ]
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[BlindStructureResponse].
# levels 전체 교체 (PUT semantics).

### 72.6 PUT /api/v1/payout-structures/{id} — update payout (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/payout-structures/{{payout_structure_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Payout Structure"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[PayoutStructureResponse].

### 72.7 PUT /api/v1/flights/{id} — update flight (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/flights/{{flight_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flight_name": "Day 1A — Updated",
  "scheduled_start_at": "2026-07-01T12:00:00Z"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[FlightResponse].
# Type D 후보: .http history 에 PATCH 있음 — 본 entry 는 router PUT 정합 검증.

### 72.8 PUT /api/v1/events/{id} — update event (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/events/{{event_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_name": "Event #1 — Updated",
  "table_size": 9
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[EventResponse].

### 72.9 PUT /api/v1/configs/{id} — update config (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/configs/{{config_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "updated_value",
  "value_type": "string"
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[ConfigResponse].

### 72.10 PATCH /api/v1/decks/{id} — patch deck metadata (admin)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/decks/{{deck_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK + ApiResponse[DeckResponse].
# router 는 PATCH (RESTful partial update).

### 72.11 PUT /api/v1/tables/{id} — update table (admin)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/tables/{{table_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_name": "Featured Table — Updated",
  "seats_count": 9
}

# 예상 응답:
# 200 OK + ApiResponse[TableResponse].
# Type D drift 측정 — 일부 .http 가 PATCH /api/v1/tables/{id} 사용 중.
# 본 entry 는 router 정본 (PUT) 검증. PATCH .http 는 cycle 14 Orphan-C 결정 PR.
